Follow @4barfriday to be a part of the movement.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Damian Lillard on July 24, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'There once was a farmer who had two buckets.'.
Photo by Damian Lillard on July 24, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'He used those buckets to bring water home every day.'.
Photo by Damian Lillard on July 24, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'One of the buckets had a crack and leaked continuously. The other was perfect and never spilled a drop.'.
Photo by Damian Lillard on July 24, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'As time passed the cracked bucket became sad about the leaked water... He decided to speak with the farmer.'.
Photo by Damian Lillard on July 24, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Upon learning that he was sad the farmer asked the bucket to join him on a walk.'.

Photo by Damian Lillard on July 24, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'They walked down the same path as always... But this time the farmer pointed out all of the wonderful life that had sprung up around them.'.

Photo by Damian Lillard on July 24, 2021. May be a cartoon of text that says 'He explained to the bucket that he was responsible for all of this beauty... If he hadn't leaked water every day the plants would never have arown.'.
Photo by Damian Lillard on July 24, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'The bucket realized that, despite his flaws... He still helped those around him grow ..Even when he wasn't aware of it.'.
